msgid ""
"Once a resource has been loaded by the engine, it is cached in memory for"
" faster access, and future calls to the :ref:`load "
"<class_ResourceLoader_method_load>` method will use the cached version. "
"The cached resource can be overridden by using "
":ref:`Resource.take_over_path <class_Resource_method_take_over_path>` on "
"a new resource for that same path."
msgstr ""

