msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_resourceloader.rst:116
msgid ""
"The registered :ref:`ResourceFormatLoader <class_ResourceFormatLoader>`\\"
" s are queried sequentially to find the first one which can handle the "
"file's extension, and then attempt loading. If loading fails, the "
"remaining ResourceFormatLoaders are also attempted."
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_resourceloader.rst:120
msgid ""
"If ``no_cache`` is ``true``, the resource cache will be bypassed and the "
"resource will be loaded anew. Otherwise, the cached resource will be "
"returned if it exists."
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_resourceloader.rst:122
msgid ""
"Returns an empty resource if no ResourceFormatLoader could handle the "
"file."
msgstr ""

